---
name: Booking Flow Logic
description: Client booking rules, time slots, and WhatsApp confirmation
type: feature
---
- Public flow at `/agendar`.
- Bookable days are Friday and Saturday only.
- Monday through Thursday are walk-in only: hide time slots, show the exact warning “Meios de semana atendemos exclusivamente por ordem de chegada. Agendamentos disponíveis apenas para finais de semana!”, and provide “Agendar para o Final de Semana” shortcut to the next Friday.
- 30 min slots from 08:00, dynamic 14-day window.
- Excludes Sundays, past times, 12:30, 13:00, 13:30.
- Confirmation via WhatsApp: `wa.me/5577981302545`.
- Returning guests skip identification (stored in LocalStorage `onetwo_guest_name`).
- WhatsApp message format:
  📌 *NOVO AGENDAMENTO*
  👤 *Cliente:* [NOME]
  ✂️ *Serviço:* [SERVIÇO]
  📅 *Data:* [DATA]
  ⏰ *Horário:* [HORÁRIO]
  ✅ *Agendamento realizado pelo App!
- Occupied slots: 'Reservado' at 40% opacity gray (#808080).
